data.description: Perfect for the first time home buyer.  The entire interior of the home has been recently renovated. The renovations and upgrades include, New grey Luxury Vinyl flooring throughout, freshly painted throughout, New Shaker kitchen cabinets with white Quartz countertops in the kitchen. The bathrooms all have new vanities. Upon entering you are greeted with the openness of the vaulted ceiling in the living area. A double sided fireplace, one side facing living room and the other facing dining room, perfect for those chilly days.  You then pass through to the large updated open concept kitchen with breakfast bar seating at the island. The home offers 5 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, Great for a large/growing family. The Master boasts a vaulted ceiling, bathroom with his and hers sinks, shower and jacuzzi soaking tub.  Indoor Laundry room, which is a must. 2 car attached garage.  Backyard offers great potential with a covered Aluma wood patio. Concrete pad for basketball A large shed & gated RV parking with enough room to park extra cars, boat, and an RV.  Solar panels.   This is the perfect home in the Spring Valley Ridge Community, just waiting for a new family. Great location, close distance to freeway, schools, shops, restaurants.  *****Seller open to giving buyers concessions toward closing cost or rate buy down******
